import React from "react";
import {
    Container,
    Form,
    FormGroup,
    Input,
    Label,
    Col,
    FormText,
    Button
} from 'reactstrap';
const SignUp = () => {
  return (
    <Container className="p-5">
      <Form>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="name" sm={3}>
            Name
          </Label>
          <Col sm={9}>
            <Input
              id="name"
              name="name"
              placeholder="Enter your name"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="empid" sm={3}>
            Employee Id
          </Label>
          <Col sm={9}>
            <Input
              id="empid"
              name="empid"
              placeholder="Enter your Employee id"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="username" sm={3}>
            Email Id
          </Label>
          <Col sm={9}>
            <Input
              id="username"
              name="username"
              placeholder="Enter your Email id"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        <FormGroup row>
          <Label for="phone" sm={3}>
            Phone
          </Label>
          <Col sm={9}>
            <Input
              id="phone"
              name="phone"
              placeholder="Enter your Contact number"
              type="text"
            />
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
        
        <FormGroup check row>
          <Col
            sm={{
              offset: 2,
              size: 10,
            }}
          >
            <Button>Submit</Button>
          </Col>
        </FormGroup>
      </Form>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default SignUp;
